# Auto Clicker

This is an auto clicker application for Windows with customizable options.

## Features
- Set click interval (seconds)
- Set number of clicks
- Choose click type (left or right)
- Option to keep clicking until stopped
- Customizable start/stop hotkey
- Settings are saved between sessions

## Usage
- Download the executable file from the releases section.
- Run the executable.
- Set your desired options in the GUI.
- Use the hotkey to start/stop the auto clicker.

## Download
You can download the latest version of the executable from the [Releases](https://github.com/your-repo/auto-clicker/releases) section.

## Building from Source
To build the executable from the source code, you need Python and the required libraries:
```sh
pip install pyautogui tk keyboard pyinstaller
